metadata.name: Dont step on the Painting
metadata.description:
3070*4220px JPG.

Each of our Artificial Intelligence (AI) generated artwork is a unique NFT piece and you'll own a collectible that nobody else in the world will ever have. As AI NFTs continues to advance in the future and become more popular, you secure one of its early creations. Certified forever on the Ethereum blockchain.

Artificial Intelligence captures eyes and mind. We are using AI computer programs with machine learning algorithms to create abstract digital art paintings that would be impossible for humans to create on their own.
